title: TO1: Identify CBRN Threat Categories
body: On completion of this section, you will be able to identify the four categories of CBRN threats and their distinguishing characteristics.

title: TO2: Apply Immediate Actions on Detection
displayTitle: TO2: Apply Immediate Actions on Detection
body: On completion of this section, you will be able to state the correct immediate actions to take upon detection of a CBRN hazard.

title: Assessment
body: Complete the following assessment to demonstrate your understanding of CBRN awareness fundamentals.
